text: John Leslie Toohey (4 March 1930 - 9 April 2015) was an Australian judge. He served as the Justice of the High Court of Australia from 6 February 1987 to 2 February 1998. Toohey was born in rural Western Australia. He died on 9 April 2015, aged 85. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Australian judges Category:Australian lawyers Category:Politicians from Western Australia Category:King's Counsel
